net.sf.tweety.logics.commons.syntax.interfaces

Interface ClassicalFormula

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Conjuctable, Disjunctable, net.sf.tweety.commons.Formula, Invertable, ProbabilityAware, SimpleLogicalFormula

    public interface ClassicalFormula
extends Disjunctable, Conjuctable, Invertable, ProbabilityAware
    This interface models a classical formula, i.e. a formula that can be connected to other classical formulas using AND and OR and where the complement is well-defined.
    Author:
    Matthias Thimm, Tim Janus
